{"type":null,"faqId":21643,"title":"使用手环的蓝牙耳机连接手机听歌的时候，音乐的声音是怎么处理的？","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.5833333in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:0.008333334in;margin-left:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.11111111in;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n</p>\n荣耀手环创新的使用了A2DP自动切换功能，主要的作用是对于媒体音频进行智能分配。<br>\n1)手机蓝牙正常连接手环，当蓝牙耳机在腕带上时，播放音乐，声音会从手机喇叭或者手机的有线耳机播放，不会通过蓝牙耳机播放。<br>\n2)当手机播放音乐的过程中，把蓝牙耳机从腕带上取下，声音会通过蓝牙耳机播放。<br>\n3)当手机音乐通过手环蓝牙耳机播放时，将蓝牙耳机重新放到腕带上，手机的音乐播放会自动暂停（部分媒体播放器可能不支持）。<br>\n该功能华为已经申请专利！<br>\n<p>\n</p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":209,"faqType":"连接与配对","useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5344","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Connection-Paring","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1427334706000,"seriesProductName":"B1-Honor","visitedTimes":263,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀手环,B1,活动提醒,活动,提醒","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}